                        <interp inst="t18380618-name-391" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM KNIGHTLEY</persName>
                  </hi>. I was with Mr. Rowley, and saw the prisoner drop the handkerchief, or throw it from his side—I took it up, and gave it to the watchman.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I saw the handkerchief lying down, but I did not throw it down.</p>
